ockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解話個印度佬奶共？ <br />\n<br />\n佢做過咩野</blockquote><br />\n同問，我睇佢做訪問都好中肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有睇佢專欄 周不時暗串大陸架喎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/article/2072637/facts-hypocrisy-and-outcry-over-police-abuse-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fhong-kong%2Farticle%2F2072637%2Ffacts-hypocrisy-and-outcry-over-police-abuse-hong-kong&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6X9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=d1177882\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/article/2072637/facts-hypocrisy-and-outcry-over-police-abuse-hong-kong</a><br />\n<br />\n.....失去認同 肢離破碎<br />\n艱難地步入2017年，褚簡寧覺得香港已淪為失去認同、肢離破碎的城市。港人抱怨社會兩極化、住屋負擔不起、青年人理想破滅、內地干預、失去競爭力，怨盡一切，就是不怨自己有問題。<br />\n<br />\n歸根究柢，褚簡寧相信所有錯誤源於根深蒂固的追求「真民主」想法。他分析指，港人自欺欺人地認為「高度自治」等同「自決」，以為北京不會介入任何選舉，亦自欺欺人地覺得所謂的「真民主」會保護我們，以為可以擺脫內地的影響。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/58723/page/6\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/58723/page/6</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://du-uu.com/article/58b99c5a24f63300105798c3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdu-uu.com%2Farticle%2F58b99c5a24f63300105798c3&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6X9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=00f70ae7\" target=\"_blank\">https://du-uu.com/article/58b99c5a24f63300105798c3</a>"},{"pid":"a87b2e3bedaf86a32a1e65c75510ee7ee594288a","tid":189892,"uid":12720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T04:57:13.000Z","msg":"想知tvb新聞主播有冇3，5雞一個月？"},{"pid":"b4f3b7406bc615e87afde030d26c5dcd3143be05","tid":189892,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T05:15:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cd7156ba3ac1593fdaa50ba83b4ac3ac2730bf28","tid":189892,"uid":516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T05:17:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想知tvb新聞主播有冇3，5雞一個月？</blockquote><br />\n主播先兩雞，當年小飛俠，依家唔知</blockq